(3869,	2,	'2014-10-04T14:00:00+0100-1539005676329501@hubcal.axwax.uk',	'WORKSHOP IS FULL Fermented Foods Workshop',	'Bookings for this workshop are now closed, there is now a first come, first served waiting list BY EMAIL request ONLY to <a href=\"mailto:wildfoodie@gmail.com\">wildfoodie@gmail.com</a>. If you haven\'t received a payment acknowledgement from me please get in touch as soon as possible! thanks!  <br/> <br/>Discover the health benefitsof  fermented foods such as Beetroot Kvass and Sauerkraut with health writer and blogger, Gill Jacobs. After a delicious shared lunch  featuring some of Gill\'s favourite fermented food recipes, we\'ll get to work and prepare our own batch to take home with veggies from the farm.  <br/>Price: earlybird  £20 until 15th September. £25 from 16th September. Up to 5  \'pay what you can\' places available for those on benefits or unwaged. <br/>Transport to Lode: bike posse from Cambridge and lift share available,  Also  the  No 10 bus from Drummer St to Lode Church.  <br/>for full details and to book please message Jacky Sutton-Adam',	'2014-10-04 15:00:00',	'2014-10-04 17:30:00',	'https://www.facebook.com/events/1539005676329501/',	'Willow Farm, Lode Fen, Lode, Cambridge CB25 9HF',	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	'',	'',	''),
