(16895,	6,	'12270-1454958000-1455055200@centreforglobalequality.org',	'Take part in FameLab Cambridge!',	'FameLab is an international communications competition designed to engage and entertain by breaking down science, technology and engineering concepts into three minutes talks for a public audience. <br/> <br/>Participants have three minutes to present any scientific, engineering, mathematical or medical topic, only using props they carry on to the stage (and no powerpoint!) <br/>  <br/>10 applicants from the heats will be chosen to progress to FameLab final on 8th March at Cambridge Junction from 7pm. <br/>  <br/>Entrants must be 21 years old or older, studying or working in science, engineering, technology, medicine or mathematics.',	'2016-02-08 19:00:00',	'2016-02-09 22:00:00',	'http://centreforglobalequality.org/event/take-part-in-famelab-cambridge/',	'',	'2016-01-13 12:31:08',	'',	'',	'http://centreforglobalequality.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Famelab.png'),
