(16897,	6,	'12276-1455899400-1456075800@centreforglobalequality.org',	'Social Venture Weekend at Cambridge Judge Business',	'Bookings are now open for the University of Cambridge\'s next Social Venture Weekend at Cambridge Judge Business School. <br/> <br/>The Social Venture Weekend offers two and a half days of intensive world-class training for people with an ambition to set up or grow a business dedicated to making positive social impact. The training, provided by Cambridge Judge Business School, helps emerging social ventures refine their idea and develop their business plan and pitch. Participants also have the opportunity to share and test ideas with other social entrepreneurs, learn from the experiences of successful entrepreneurs and pitch their idea to a panel of experienced advisors, investors and entrepreneurs.',	'2016-02-19 16:30:00',	'2016-02-21 17:30:00',	'http://centreforglobalequality.org/event/social-venture-weekend-at-cambridge-judge-business/',	'Trumping ton Street, Cambridge, Cambridgeshire, CB2 1AG, United Kingdom',	'2016-01-13 13:24:15',	'',	'',	'http://centreforglobalequality.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/JBS.png'),
