(16899,	6,	'10792-1457308800-1458518399@centreforglobalequality.org',	'Cambridge Science Festival',	'Throughout two weeks of lively science talks, demonstrations, exhibitions, theatre, comedy, art and much more, the Science Festival gives the opportunity to bring voices into the scientific conversation: Nobel Prize winners, Fellows of the Royal Society and advisors to Government, usually joined by a selection of school children and young researchers to explain innovative areas of science and technology. <br/> <br/>This festival will open the doors of the University of Cambridge to the public, including charities, with an opportunity to get inspired on a scientific level by innovative solutions for international development.',	'2016-03-07 00:00:00',	'2016-03-20 00:00:00',	'http://centreforglobalequality.org/event/cambridge-science-festival/',	'Trumpington Street, Cambridge, CB2 1RP, United Kingdom',	'2015-07-21 00:00:00',	'Cambridge%20Science%20Festival',	'csf@admin.cam.ac.uk',	''),
