(17916,	5,	'2016-02-11T19:30:00+0000-223779921290619@green-calendar.gigx.co.uk',	'Food for Thought',	'Tired of smalltalk? Looking for provoking conversations? A place to sound deeper than you may or may not actually be? <br/> <br/>Weâ€™re very excited to invite you to our first Food for Thought dinner of 2016. Alongside our usual evening of meaningful interactions and interesting conversations, we\'ll be serving up South African fare by Now Now with 3 courses for £15. MENU POSTED ON FB EVENT PAGE, please look through and indicate which main course (and whether you\'d like it bunny chow style or with rice) and desert option you\'d like on the tilt sign up.  <br/> <br/>You will be seated with people you havenâ€™t had the chance to meet before and given a menu of questions big and small to explore together.  <br/> <br/>Please sign up and pay using this link <a href=\'http://til.tt/Rilt\' target=\'_blank\'>http://til.tt/Rilt</a>  <br/>Bookings limited to 24 seats and end Feb 8th. <br/> <br/>Hope to see you there! <br/>Hosted by Muse and Cambridge Hub',	'2016-02-11 19:30:00',	'2016-02-11 21:30:00',	'https://www.facebook.com/events/223779921290619/',	'Novi, Cambridge',	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	'',	'',	'https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/t31.0-8/s720x720/12622152_1031192153607991_1220240657159215406_o.png'),
