(26473,	5,	'2016-02-26T17:00:00+0000-922737674490683@green-calendar.gigx.co.uk',	'Green Officer meeting- SHARE IDEAS',	'CALLING all JCR and MCR green officers: this will be a meet-up/networking event.... an opportunity to speak to other Green (and Ethical)officers, share ideas, get inspired and support each other. <br/> <br/>Not too long, slightly informal, I\'ll provide oranges.  <br/> <br/>We will also quickly introduce what CUSU Ethical Affairs, the Cambridge HUB and the Environment and Energy Section of the University are doing and how we can support all of you.  <br/> <br/>\'Living sustainably will never be someting done by individuals- it\'s what we need to do all together. So come along, and help bring sustainable living and ideas to your own and other colleges.\' <br/> <br/>If you have any ideas/questions, feel free to contact me (Laura Schubert) at <a href=\"mailto:environment@cambridgehub.org\">environment@cambridgehub.org</a>',	'2016-02-26 17:00:00',	'2016-02-26 17:45:00',	'https://www.facebook.com/events/922737674490683/',	'Emmanuel College, Timmy Hele Room (Queens building)',	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	'',	'',	'https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpl1/v/t1.0-9/10254049_808186082621218_3263013194733649969_n.jpg?oh=0657559cdf0a932c7f3b49e313f6752d&oe=575C6AF7'),
