(28534,	29,	'e1048214168576682@facebook.com',	'Vote Angus Satow for CUSU President',	'Hey everyone, I\'m running for CUSU President! As President I will do what I\'ve shown I can do over the last year, and fight for a better Cambridge - more resources for the Disability Resource Centre and the Counselling Service, better co-ordinated and supported liberation campaigns, greater student representation and student power. Let\'sengage with our student union andmake things better for everyone. VOTE NOW - <a href=\'https://www.vote.cusu.cam.ac.uk/cusuandgu/15-16/cusugu/\' target=\'_blank\'>https://www.vote.cusu.cam.ac.uk/cusuandgu/15-16/cusugu/</a>  <br/> <br/><a href=\'https://www.vote.cusu.cam.ac.uk/cusuandgu/15-16/cusugu/\' target=\'_blank\'>https://www.vote.cusu.cam.ac.uk/cusuandgu/15-16/cusugu/</a> ',	'2016-02-25 08:00:00',	'2016-03-03 19:00:00',	'http://www.facebook.com/events/1048214168576682/',	'Cambridge University Students\' Union (CUSU)',	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	'Cambridge University Students\' Union (CUSU)',	'noreply@facebookmail.com',	''),
